# Paths the `tauri dev` file watcher must NOT watch.
#
# `build.rs` stages the freshly-built `bulwarkctl` into `binaries/` as an externalBin sidecar on
# every build. Without this ignore, that write lands inside the watched `src-tauri/` tree, so the
# watcher fires, rebuilds, `build.rs` re-copies the sidecar, the watcher fires again — an infinite
# rebuild loop where the app window never opens. The staged sidecar is a build *output*; nothing
# about it should ever trigger a rebuild.
binaries/
